text: Gonystylus nervosus is a species of plant in the Thymelaeaceae family. It is a tree endemic to Borneo where it is confined to Sarawak. ==References== nervosus Category:Endemic flora of Borneo Category:Trees of Borneo Category:Flora of Sarawak Category:Vulnerable plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
